bour.camus.gameofgooses.models.cells

Class DepartureCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • bour.camus.gameofgooses.models.cells.DepartureCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICell

    public class DepartureCell
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICell
    DepartureCell represents the first case of a Board. It is the only cell that can contain several Players.
    Author:
    Armand BOUR, Tristan CAMUS
